# UX Guidelines (agent-ux.md)

When changing colors, layout, or controls, follow `agent-ux.md`. Key rules:

## Color
- Use CSS variables (`var(--bg-primary)`, `var(--accent)`) — never hardcode hex
- Status: 2xx green, 3xx blue, 4xx orange, 5xx red
- Maintain contrast for text on backgrounds

## Icon vs Text
- **Icon:** Universal actions (Send, Save, Settings, Close), space-constrained (tab close, +)
- **Text:** Primary/rare actions ("Create collection", "Save as"), when icon is ambiguous
- **Icon + tooltip:** Secondary actions; add `aria-label` for icon-only buttons

## Usability
- Hover/focus states on all clickables
- Loading feedback for async actions
- Visible labels on form inputs
- Logical keyboard tab order; Escape closes modals

## Consistency
- Use `--radius-sm/md/lg`, `--transition-fast/base`
- Match existing button/modal styles in the codebase
